{"tid":1622752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋以後遊行抗爭可唔可以咁樣做","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T17:21:40.000Z","uid":144621,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3054d340e6c5afdf8328ac710bd67b66b7246ca","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"逢星期六日港島例牌都有大型遊行，但係因為地形同埋交通關係次次都損手爛腳返屋企。最近依排18區開花俾咗我一個小小嘅啟示。就係港島大型遊行照去不過全程和埋非，純粹谷大人數。返到自己地頭就先開花，咁樣對各位手足會唔會好啲，至少唔會因為唔熟地形落單，壞處可能唔夠人手。大家討論一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9851618ab0d24528d2d6724ba3c971b8ea38e54","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83e57798d15b863cdf9fb7be53d76cbe2574217d","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b25e63666c6dd03830e839f59148e2f6f2be0842","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"679590240d4c070761681684be646abb13e763bc","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f28116bf013a73422b8975218bb8d08a75c571f6","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d116bdbff6a1105aa6022a69797bff4e2fcadc7b","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"bbfea269fad734a3e7acb837cc9731d0037436d3","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:10:06.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"940fe454a6a3bc27dd959cd1da62b32e8041ccde","tid":1622752,"uid":144621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"5b659f3c083b22e029a51c334e0e28068315cdee","tid":1622752,"uid"